Make your Sneakers Waterproof, Stain Proof & Dirt Proof with this Hack using 5 Rupees only. 

What you’ll Need

1.  Candle
2. Blow Dryer

Steps

1. Apply Candle all over the Sneaker.
2. Blow Dry till the wax disappears from the Sneaker. 
3. Let the Sneaker rest for 5 minutes.
